media:group.media:description:

The European Union itself has promised that Armenians will one day be able to travel to Europe visa-free, like their Georgian neighbours. But as of now, the process for Armenian citizens to get EU visas remains arduous. It is commonplace for people not to receive responses prior to their planned travel date, causing disruptions to peoplesโ travel, education and work plans.
